1. Can you share a specific example of a challenging situation you've faced in your current role and how you navigated through it?

2. How do you prioritize tasks and manage your time effectively in a fast-paced work environment?

3. What do you believe sets you apart from other candidates in terms of your skills and experience for this position?

4. How do you stay updated on industry trends and developments to ensure your skills remain relevant and competitive?
I work hard to learn new things as much as possible  and that helps me keep up I tried to learn new AI tools to ask questions and that's how I keep up

That's great to hear that you are proactive in learning new AI tools! Can you share with me a specific AI tool or technology that you found particularly interesting or useful in your work? How has it impacted your productivity or the way you approach tasks in your field?
